  "abstract": "Pursuant to the provisions of the Privacy Act of 1974, notice is given that the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (Board) proposes to establish a new system of records, entitled BGFRS- 45, ``FRB--Debt Collection Records.'' BGFRS-45 includes records concerning debts owed to the Board or to the United States (including but not limited to restitution collectible by the United States) that arise out of the Board's operations or other activities, and records concerning the Board's effo",
